WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:47.430 --> 00:01:37.680
Dr. Warren has already talked to you 

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:45.860
about the different centers that we have within
ourselves, and you can see how beautifully

00:01:45.860 --> 00:01:56.390
they are placed and how gradually when the
Kundalini rises, how She enlightens the innermost

00:01:56.390 --> 00:02:05.350
core of the centers.

00:02:05.350 --> 00:02:17.510
There are three channels in the central channel,
and the innermost channel is used by Kundalini

00:02:17.510 --> 00:02:21.640
to pierce through for the first time.

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:35.101
You can imagine Kundalini to be made of many
strands of energy tied together just like

00:02:35.101 --> 00:02:50.430
a rope, and as the chakras start opening more
strands start getting awakened and they pierce

00:02:50.430 --> 00:03:02.160
through these six centers; but if a person
after Realization just thinks that he has

00:03:02.160 --> 00:03:07.530
got the Realization, then he doesn't have
to bother about it, may lose it for the time

00:03:07.530 --> 00:03:15.950
being, for quite some time I should say, and
he'll have to work much harder to re-establish

00:03:15.950 --> 00:03:20.799
his Self Realization.

00:03:20.799 --> 00:03:29.170
I've seen many-a-times when we give Realization
to people they say, “Yes, we have felt it.”

00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:39.130
They did feel it, everything happens, and
then they loose it because they have not established

00:03:39.130 --> 00:03:47.600
their Realization properly, for which luckily
in every place wherever I go I see to it that

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:57.859
we already have a center established, then
you can go to that center and you can learn

00:03:57.859 --> 00:04:04.109
from them how to establish your Realization.

00:04:04.109 --> 00:04:09.040
That is a very, very important time which
must be taken into consideration.

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:18.389
There was a lady who had cancer, she was cured
of her cancer, she was perfectly all right

00:04:18.389 --> 00:04:30.169
and she went back to her family, she was doing
very well, and after some time - a year or

00:04:30.169 --> 00:04:37.500
so - she came back with another disease of
a very serious nature.

00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:43.300
So I asked her, “How is it that you are
cured of cancer, now you get another disease?

00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:45.790
Did you do anything about it?”

00:04:45.790 --> 00:04:51.199
“No, Mother, I went back from here, everybody
says, ‘You are looking very fine.’

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:57.720
They are all right, they were all quite surprised
how I was cured, and I never bothered to do

00:04:57.720 --> 00:04:59.840
anything about it.”

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:02.180
So she got another trouble.

00:05:02.180 --> 00:05:09.720
You go on like this, you cure one thing then
you again cure another thing.

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:17.169
Like little children, you clean them, then
again they get out and soil their clothes,

00:05:17.169 --> 00:05:22.750
again they are back in the bathroom, then
again you clean them, again they do the same

00:05:22.750 --> 00:05:23.750
thing.

00:05:23.750 --> 00:05:30.650
So you have to mature, after Realization you
must in all wisdom and sensible behavior,

00:05:30.650 --> 00:05:37.280
you must mature of it, otherwise it is a big
headache to Me and big headache to you, and

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:46.180
you can be quite lost also with it, because
if a seed is half-sprouted it is of no use

00:05:46.180 --> 00:05:47.610
at all.

00:05:47.610 --> 00:05:55.409
So if you want that you should really have
the complete bliss of Self Realization, you

00:05:55.409 --> 00:05:58.650
have to become a little serious person about
it.

00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:04.960
Shallow temperament is not going to help you,
or looking at it as if like another guru shopping

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:08.180
business it is not going to work out.

00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:13.960
You have to work to see that you establish
yourself, till you have established you are

00:06:13.960 --> 00:06:19.729
not to work on other people but once you are
established you can start working on other

00:06:19.729 --> 00:06:21.970
people, giving them Realization.

00:06:21.970 --> 00:06:29.219
There is no need then for you to bother that
you will catch from others, or anything; but

00:06:29.219 --> 00:06:33.229
before that you should not try to help others.

00:06:33.229 --> 00:06:37.159
First help yourself, selfishness to begin
with.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:43.710
Unless and until you are all right and you
know all the methods of protecting yourself,

00:06:43.710 --> 00:06:53.120
you are not to indulge into Sahaja Yoga practices
which helps others.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:57.530
But when you become an expert, when you have
an expertise then you should do it.

00:06:57.530 --> 00:07:02.629
Like a mechanic who doesn’t know how to
repair a car, they spoil it more.

00:07:02.629 --> 00:07:07.490
So better become an expert for which you don't
have to pay anything, you don't have to do

00:07:07.490 --> 00:07:13.759
much about it but only to understand how you
have to move the Kundalini within you, how

00:07:13.759 --> 00:07:22.680
you have to establish it back, what problems
you have and how you have to cure.

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:27.520
You will be surprised you won't be aware of
problems that you have.

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:32.639
One gentleman came and told Me, “Mother
everyone is coming and asking me, ‘what

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:35.069
about your father, what's the problem?’”

00:07:35.069 --> 00:07:37.629
I said, “Everybody said the same?”

00:07:37.629 --> 00:07:38.949
He said, “Yes.”

00:07:38.949 --> 00:07:41.439
I said, “I also want to know, what about
your father?”

00:07:41.439 --> 00:07:47.759
He said, “My father died very early in life,
and I always had a feeling that I had no father.”

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:54.770
That can be cured, and he developed asthma
with it, so everybody knows, those who know

00:07:54.770 --> 00:07:59.159
one thing that is the truth about you.

00:07:59.159 --> 00:08:03.020
All of them will say the same thing, even
if it is a small child, he will also come

00:08:03.020 --> 00:08:06.770
and ask you that “Is your father all right?”

00:08:06.770 --> 00:08:12.439
Because if he knows that this center, this
center on the right hand side means the father.

00:08:12.439 --> 00:08:19.389
So he will also say the same and then he will
come and ask you, “what about your father?”

00:08:19.389 --> 00:08:27.180
It is so remarkable sometimes the way people
see these things that they can't believe it,

00:08:27.180 --> 00:08:31.569
but this is nothing, what you get is just
a wee bit of it.

00:08:31.569 --> 00:08:39.729
But as Kundalini rises, on every center you
start getting the light of that center.

00:08:39.729 --> 00:08:50.350
At the first center you get back your innocence,
your eyes become innocent, your behavior becomes

00:08:50.350 --> 00:08:56.890
innocent, you are not filled with lust and
greed, you don't look at things with lust

00:08:56.890 --> 00:09:03.850
and greed, but you look at things with innocence,
which is a very big thing that people have

00:09:03.850 --> 00:09:10.070
lost and that you get back and such a person
develops many qualities.

00:09:10.070 --> 00:09:18.160
One of them is that such a person is full
of fragrance, such a person has a tremendous

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:29.529
gravity, tremendous gravity, and such a person
has tremendous dynamism, and attraction is

00:09:29.529 --> 00:09:34.370
a bad word so I don't want to use it, but
magnetical.

00:09:34.370 --> 00:09:43.380
His magnets is awakened within him, this is
the center of your magnet of the earth.

00:09:43.380 --> 00:09:51.431
Such a person develops a tremendous sense
of roots and sense of direction, you place

00:09:51.431 --> 00:09:53.750
him anywhere he will know where to go.

00:09:53.750 --> 00:09:59.339
Like birds, you place birds anywhere they
know which side is north, south, east, west.

00:09:59.339 --> 00:10:09.011
In the same way you also develop your lost
innocence and your magnet within you by which

00:10:09.011 --> 00:10:16.230
you have proper direction; but the highest
of all you develop the proper direction to

00:10:16.230 --> 00:10:19.910
wisdom which is the wise thing to do.

00:10:19.910 --> 00:10:26.610
You just don't do stupid things, you just
don't do, even if you ever try to do it, you

00:10:26.610 --> 00:10:32.170
will not do it, because you know it is so
stupid, just you don't do it.

00:10:32.170 --> 00:10:40.250
I mean it is so simple to be wise than to
be stupid, because if you have to be stupid

00:10:40.250 --> 00:10:48.240
you have to go out of the way to be stupid
and idiotic; but if you want to be normal

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:50.610
and wise is the easiest thing to do.

00:10:50.610 --> 00:11:00.399
But what people do is to do things that would
make them more and more stupid, nonsensical,

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:09.029
because also some people told Me they do it,
the reason being they think they have a nuisance

00:11:09.029 --> 00:11:10.029
value.

00:11:10.029 --> 00:11:14.430
Like in London now we have one funny stuff
going on, they call it what?

00:11:14.430 --> 00:11:15.430
“Punk rock.”

00:11:15.430 --> 00:11:17.389
You see, it's a funny stuff.

00:11:17.389 --> 00:11:23.630
Now poor kids they don't know what they are
doing it, and I think the only value of that

00:11:23.630 --> 00:11:34.570
punk rock system is this: that they try to
sort of make a nuisance out of them so that

00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:39.480
people feel attracted towards them or sort
of a significance out of them.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:46.389
But when you become a realized soul you realize
your significance, because you understand

00:11:46.389 --> 00:11:54.160
you are part and parcel of the whole and that
your significance is to give Realization to

00:11:54.160 --> 00:12:00.649
others, the highest of highest, that's what
you have to do now you are a saint, and that’s

00:12:00.649 --> 00:12:10.269
how the whole attitude of cheapiness, of outward
shallowness finishes and you become a serene,

00:12:10.269 --> 00:12:11.370
dignified personality.

00:12:11.370 --> 00:12:18.959
This is not possible through any sermon, any
lecture, it's only possible when the Kundalini

00:12:18.959 --> 00:12:27.000
rises you become like a very dignified child,
very dignified child.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:35.770
I've seen one beautiful painting done of Mother
Mary being taught first time.

00:12:35.770 --> 00:12:42.210
You see Her as a child, She is a very dignified
personality, as a child, She is about ten

00:12:42.210 --> 00:12:43.269
years of age.

00:12:43.269 --> 00:12:49.640
I've seen My own grandchildren who are not
very old but extremely dignified.

00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:52.899
They walk like kings, behave like kings.

00:12:52.899 --> 00:12:58.149
In every behavior you find there's such a
dignity, they'll never do something shallow,

00:12:58.149 --> 00:13:02.670
they never ask for anything, they never weep
for anything, they never cry for anything,

00:13:02.670 --> 00:13:08.079
they are so dignified and they understand
it so well what is dignity is.

00:13:08.079 --> 00:13:14.230
I don't have to tell them, because they are
born realized, in the same way you become,

00:13:14.230 --> 00:13:18.680
nobody has to tell you that “do this, or
do that,” but you understand that you must

00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:21.220
have self-respect.

00:13:21.220 --> 00:13:26.690
This happens to you automatically, this is
actualization, nobody has to tell you that

00:13:26.690 --> 00:13:28.279
“you be dignified,” you just become.

00:13:28.279 --> 00:13:33.560
I've seen people who were absolutely absurd,
even from this punk rock we got some people

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:39.360
and they were so changed that people could
not recognize them, but one thing bad has

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:45.509
happened with this punk rock that they put
some sort of dye in their head and since then

00:13:45.509 --> 00:13:52.220
their eyes became very weak, because these
dyes I think made the optic globe covered

00:13:52.220 --> 00:13:58.060
with some sort of a color and you can't see
properly, and the eyes became very weak and

00:13:58.060 --> 00:14:04.220
it took some time for us to remove the effect
of those dyes from their head.

00:14:04.220 --> 00:14:06.370
We go headlong, “what's wrong?”

00:14:06.370 --> 00:14:12.279
There is nothing wrong in this world if it
is a stupid fool, but for a wise man there

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:17.889
are very many things which are absolutely
wrong, and there are very many things which

00:14:17.889 --> 00:14:24.170
are absolutely correct, so you develop your
wisdom by this first center.

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:31.730
Now as the Kundalini rises She enlightens
your second center which we can call as the

00:14:31.730 --> 00:14:34.920
Swadishthan Chakra for the time being, though
it is the third center.

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:39.410
But second center, you become extremely creative,
extremely creative.

00:14:39.410 --> 00:14:46.009
I know of a gentleman who came to Me, he had
no job.

00:14:46.009 --> 00:14:48.649
And he said, “Mother, I have no job and
what should I do?”

00:14:48.649 --> 00:14:51.230
I said, “All right, what do you want to
do?”

00:14:51.230 --> 00:14:52.850
He said, “Whatever you say.”

00:14:52.850 --> 00:14:56.560
I said, “All right, why don't you become
an interior decorator?”

00:14:56.560 --> 00:14:58.399
He said, “Me?

00:14:58.399 --> 00:15:02.949
I don't know what is a teak wood, I don’t
know what is a rose wood, how am I to become

00:15:02.949 --> 00:15:03.949
an interior decorator?”

00:15:03.949 --> 00:15:06.360
I said, “You just use your vibrations.”

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:11.480
And you'll be surprised he earned million
of rupees out of that profession because you

00:15:11.480 --> 00:15:20.009
become extremely creative, your sense of creation
becomes so subtle and so beautiful that you

00:15:20.009 --> 00:15:26.160
start understanding art at such a high level
that people don't know how, when you are not

00:15:26.160 --> 00:15:29.250
educated in art, how you can do it.

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:34.670
I went to Japan once, and they were having
an Ikebana competition or something, so I

00:15:34.670 --> 00:15:39.569
went to see the Ikebana class and they requested
Me, “Why don't you do some flower arrangements?”

00:15:39.569 --> 00:15:41.690
I said, “All right, I'll do.”

00:15:41.690 --> 00:15:48.069
I did it and I got the highest marks without
knowing a word about Ikebana, just surprise

00:15:48.069 --> 00:15:50.600
Me, I got the highest mark.

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:54.550
I can do lots of things which I've never done
before like architecture.

00:15:54.550 --> 00:16:00.879
I have built houses without doing any architecture,
I've done decorations of the houses, I've

00:16:00.879 --> 00:16:08.120
done all kinds of things without knowing how
to it, because you become you so creative.

00:16:08.120 --> 00:16:10.480
Music you start understanding so much better.

00:16:10.480 --> 00:16:16.779
There are people now in America, there's a
girl, she had a horrible hoarse voice, absolutely

00:16:16.779 --> 00:16:20.560
hoarse voice, and she always used to go out
of tune.

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:24.160
So I told her, “You shouldn’t sing songs
before Me because it’s rather funny.”

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:27.279
She said, “Mother, why don't You give me
a good voice?”

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:32.279
I said, “You just try your Vishuddhi Chakra,
if your Vishuddhi Chakra is corrected you'll

00:16:32.279 --> 00:16:34.389
be all right.”

00:16:34.389 --> 00:16:40.740
[Shri Mataji speaks aside: Why don’t you
sit down.]

00:16:40.740 --> 00:16:47.170
So the Vishuddhi Chakra was … she tried
on Vishuddhi Chakra giving vibrations, and

00:16:47.170 --> 00:16:52.760
she sings so melodiously now that I tell you
she can be a great singer.

00:16:52.760 --> 00:17:00.430
So the creativity, that also is a blessing
of your power of the Goddess of learning.

00:17:00.430 --> 00:17:05.130
Boys who could not study in the schools were
absolutely duffers.

00:17:05.130 --> 00:17:09.780
Some people brought this boy, recently I’ve
received a letter from him.

00:17:09.780 --> 00:17:13.560
When he came to Me, his father said that “He
is going to be taken out of school because

00:17:13.560 --> 00:17:17.550
he's good for nothing, he can not remember
anything, he's absolutely finished.”

00:17:17.550 --> 00:17:22.140
I said, “All right, doesn't matter, let
him take to Sahaja Yoga.”

00:17:22.140 --> 00:17:24.400
He got his Realization.

00:17:24.400 --> 00:17:28.360
Not only that he passed with first class,
but he got a scholarship.

00:17:28.360 --> 00:17:31.830
Then he passed another exam, he got a scholarship.

00:17:31.830 --> 00:17:36.080
Now he's got a very big job, at a very young
age.

00:17:36.080 --> 00:17:41.960
He wrote to Me, “Mother no one can believe
that a duffer like me has been so much highly

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:43.140
placed.”

00:17:43.140 --> 00:17:50.420
All the boys who got scholarships in Maharashtra
in schools, in colleges and universities are

00:17:50.420 --> 00:17:51.850
Sahaja Yogis.

00:17:51.850 --> 00:17:58.440
It is such a tremendous force that starts
working in you, if you try to give vibrations

00:17:58.440 --> 00:18:10.940
say to fruits or to trees or to say wheat
and such things which are very important for

00:18:10.940 --> 00:18:19.690
life, any food, you will be amazed that the
food also grows so much more and the taste

00:18:19.690 --> 00:18:23.150
is so good and it lasts you so longer.

00:18:23.150 --> 00:18:30.981
Like one gentleman tried, a university professor
in agricultural college on some wheat, some

00:18:30.981 --> 00:18:37.120
vibrations and he was amazed that when they
collected this wheat it was at least six times

00:18:37.120 --> 00:18:45.340
more than normal, and when this wheat was
stored in a big hall like this, there were

00:18:45.340 --> 00:18:53.450
so many other things, the rats who are always
a menace in India never touched that wheat.

00:18:53.450 --> 00:18:57.100
They ate all the rest of it but never touched
the wheat.

00:18:57.100 --> 00:19:05.550
Even the animals - the snails, even the tigers,
of course the dogs and the cats - understand

00:19:05.550 --> 00:19:11.070
it much more, they understand you, they know
that you are a saint.

00:19:11.070 --> 00:19:12.270
They'll never touch you, they will never trouble
you.

00:19:12.270 --> 00:19:15.900
Even a tiger sees a saint, he never attacks.

00:19:15.900 --> 00:19:20.040
You can handle a tiger very easily; this is
the power of a saint.

00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:24.630
So you develop a tremendous capacity of creativity.

00:19:24.630 --> 00:19:33.310
The greatest capacity you have then is of
creating a new human being out of a ordinary

00:19:33.310 --> 00:19:34.310
human being.

00:19:34.310 --> 00:19:41.670
This is the greatest blessing that you have,
that you transform an egg into a bird and

00:19:41.670 --> 00:19:47.380
that is the epitome, that is the spiritual
power you have, by which you can transform

00:19:47.380 --> 00:19:57.320
the whole human race into a new race which
has this fifth dimension within yourself.

00:19:57.320 --> 00:20:02.630
You can start talking on science now, we have
a scientist here and he's a done his science,

00:20:02.630 --> 00:20:08.170
he is a Doctor of Science in this and that,
in chemistry and I explained to him about

00:20:08.170 --> 00:20:12.690
this - where is the hydrogen and oxygen and
nitrogen and all that within us and he was

00:20:12.690 --> 00:20:13.690
amazed.

00:20:13.690 --> 00:20:15.980
He said, “Mother, how do you know all these
things?”

00:20:15.980 --> 00:20:19.270
I said, “I don't know how I know, but I
know.

00:20:19.270 --> 00:20:22.030
That’s what it is, you just have a look
at this.”

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:27.970
And he was amazed how I was telling him about
spiral movement and linear movement of peptose.

00:20:27.970 --> 00:20:30.110
He said that “For this I had to study so
much.”

00:20:30.110 --> 00:20:32.060
I said, “For Sahaja Yog you don't have to
study.”

00:20:32.060 --> 00:20:35.620
A little bit you know and immediately you
click the point.

00:20:35.620 --> 00:20:40.880
Now this is the second thing that you know
in your learnings, in your education you are

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:47.170
all right, but the mastery of this center
comes, the mastery of this center comes when

00:20:47.170 --> 00:20:54.470
you know the pure knowledge, the pure knowledge
of handling the Kundalini, the pure knowledge

00:20:54.470 --> 00:21:00.840
of Spirit, the pure knowledge of the blessings
of God, of Ritambhara Pragya.

00:21:00.840 --> 00:21:07.770
If you know that, that is the highest that
you achieve gradually as you grow, because

00:21:07.770 --> 00:21:14.740
when these centers starts expanding on the
sides, you start expanding in your personality,

00:21:14.740 --> 00:21:21.820
in your sensitivity and in your evolutionary
ascent, so that is how you start growing from

00:21:21.820 --> 00:21:25.710
one to another to another to another.

00:21:25.710 --> 00:21:31.460
Now the third center that we have actually,
this is the second center because the third

00:21:31.460 --> 00:21:39.020
center arises, this Swadishthana arises out
of the Nabhi, is a very, very important center,

00:21:39.020 --> 00:21:42.730
is the center of your seeking as he has told
you.

00:21:42.730 --> 00:21:50.270
Your compete priorities change, complete priorities
change, because the joy that you get out of

00:21:50.270 --> 00:22:00.000
Sahaja Yoga, the joy you get out of this meditation,
out of the feeling that grows in you all the

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:08.830
time, like a beautiful torrential rain of
joy that fills you, your life and everybody's

00:22:08.830 --> 00:22:15.280
life, you don't care for cheap type of entertainment.

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:21.140
You feel, you seek other Sahaja Yogi, you
want to meet another Sahaja Yogi, you don't

00:22:21.140 --> 00:22:22.370
want to meet anybody else.

00:22:22.370 --> 00:22:26.650
If there is an actor coming, or some big man
is coming, “All right, let him come, I'm

00:22:26.650 --> 00:22:28.410
going to see such and such person.”

00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:36.140
It is such a different personality that one
day - I will tell you how it happens - there

00:22:36.140 --> 00:22:41.280
was a girl, a diplomat, she's a diplomat who
is a realized soul and she happened to go

00:22:41.280 --> 00:22:42.910
to Sicily.

00:22:42.910 --> 00:22:46.590
And she was eating her food, suddenly she
felt there is some vibrations coming down,

00:22:46.590 --> 00:22:53.020
she looked around, the other one was also
looking at her, she said, “Are you Mataji's

00:22:53.020 --> 00:22:54.020
disciple?”

00:22:54.020 --> 00:22:56.940
And she said, “Yes, I am Mataji's child.”

00:22:56.940 --> 00:23:03.360
They both got up and just hugged and said,
“Such joy Mother in that far-fetched place

00:23:03.360 --> 00:23:05.790
of Sicily to find a Sahaja Yogi.”

00:23:05.790 --> 00:23:10.800
And then they stayed together and they wouldn’t
go anywhere else but they said, “Now this

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:11.800
is the enjoyment.”

00:23:11.800 --> 00:23:15.350
Just the company of a Sahaja Yogi is such
an enjoyment.

00:23:15.350 --> 00:23:21.100
I've seen these people when they go to India,
the people are not so rich, poor people - they

00:23:21.100 --> 00:23:25.090
have little, little huts - but when they go
they go there, you should see the love, the

00:23:25.090 --> 00:23:32.370
rapport, and that makes Me so happy, so happy,
the way they love each other, the way they

00:23:32.370 --> 00:23:38.780
understand each other, the way they help each
other and the only the company, for the first

00:23:38.780 --> 00:23:40.570
time they start enjoying.

00:23:40.570 --> 00:23:46.990
We were once in a hotel staying in Calcutta
and with two Sahaja Yogi with Me.

00:23:46.990 --> 00:23:51.540
They were in the other room, quite far away,
they could not get a room close to Me, and

00:23:51.540 --> 00:23:56.640
one gentleman came for his Realization, he
came to My feet, when he got his Realization

00:23:56.640 --> 00:24:00.750
it was a tremendous happening and they came
rushing from there.

00:24:00.750 --> 00:24:02.120
I said, “What happened?”

00:24:02.120 --> 00:24:07.121
They said, “We felt the vibrations, we felt
the vibrations from there, Mother, so we have

00:24:07.121 --> 00:24:09.490
come to receive the vibrations.”

00:24:09.490 --> 00:24:12.380
And they came and they felt the vibrations.

00:24:12.380 --> 00:24:18.850
So this man was so great that his vibrations
attracted them and they came down.

00:24:18.850 --> 00:24:24.870
They were just enjoying that as if they were
enjoying a big flower with lots of fragrance.

00:24:24.870 --> 00:24:25.940
What vibrations, what vibrations!

00:24:25.940 --> 00:24:28.510
The fellow got up and said, “Very nice.

00:24:28.510 --> 00:24:31.000
They are enjoying my vibrations.

00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:34.480
Now I'm going to enjoy your vibrations.”

00:24:34.480 --> 00:24:43.090
For the first time you start enjoying your
fellow man because everyone is a beautiful

00:24:43.090 --> 00:24:51.380
personality, a glorious, fragrant, joyful
personality; but because you cannot feel the

00:24:51.380 --> 00:24:56.650
other person, and because the other person
does not emit, you are all the time quarreling.

00:24:56.650 --> 00:25:00.950
Even husband-wife quarreling, father-mother
quarreling, this one quarreling, that quarreling.

00:25:00.950 --> 00:25:04.660
In Sahaja Yoga there is hardly any time for
people to quarrel.

00:25:04.660 --> 00:25:09.710
The other day I had a lady who came to see
Me, and she was trying to put her point and

00:25:09.710 --> 00:25:15.890
there were about five-six Sahaja Yogis, and
everybody was putting the same point and she

00:25:15.890 --> 00:25:16.890
was amazed.

00:25:16.890 --> 00:25:22.700
She said, “I've never seen such concord,
such friendship, such understanding, all of

00:25:22.700 --> 00:25:27.980
them supporting each other, nobody is cutting
anyone.”

00:25:27.980 --> 00:25:29.930
Such a society has to develop.

00:25:29.930 --> 00:25:37.960
It’s such a nourishing, soothing, invigorating
society, and you forget about getting bored,

00:25:37.960 --> 00:25:44.300
boredom goes out of life, you never get bored,
you enjoy yourself or you enjoy the company

00:25:44.300 --> 00:25:50.970
of Sahaja Yogis and it is very different level
that you come of - that is what, that land

00:25:50.970 --> 00:25:53.610
you have to reach within yourself.

00:25:53.610 --> 00:26:01.020
Now the greatest thing that happens as a result
of this center seeking, that you start seeking

00:26:01.020 --> 00:26:06.670
other seekers, you try to find out “where
is the seeker?”

00:26:06.670 --> 00:26:09.850
If you hear somebody is a seeker, you go and
see.

00:26:09.850 --> 00:26:15.780
If you hear about someone that some people
are lost there, they were seekers, but they

00:26:15.780 --> 00:26:18.310
went there lost, you all rush there.

00:26:18.310 --> 00:26:25.730
It is like a person who is like a, what you
call a guard on the seashore you know, there

00:26:25.730 --> 00:26:30.420
are guards kept for salvaging people, and
that is how you become.

00:26:30.420 --> 00:26:33.240
You suddenly see somebody sinking, you just
go.

00:26:33.240 --> 00:26:38.700
In Bombay there was a case they announce that
“there’s a lady who is going to die, if

00:26:38.700 --> 00:26:41.290
somebody can come and help her, it will be
a great thing.”

00:26:41.290 --> 00:26:44.850
They all rushed there; they saved her.

00:26:44.850 --> 00:26:51.010
Now the interests changes completely, and
you start really helping people and not feeling

00:26:51.010 --> 00:26:56.540
that you are helping them, not at all.

00:26:56.540 --> 00:27:02.100
But the surrounding portion of that, which
is the void, is the best, which is affected

00:27:02.100 --> 00:27:08.810
by your awakening, that you become the virtue
itself.

00:27:08.810 --> 00:27:16.710
Nobody has to tell you that you be virtuous,
when you are awakened you become a virtuous

00:27:16.710 --> 00:27:27.670
person, you enjoy your virtues, you enjoy
being good, you enjoy being nice, you really

00:27:27.670 --> 00:27:29.120
enjoy it.

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:35.690
And that enjoyment comes to you as a blessing
because the virtue itself is so strengthening,

00:27:35.690 --> 00:27:47.941
so powerful that anyone who is harmed or troubled
or tortured or put down, you stand up, you

00:27:47.941 --> 00:27:53.100
are not afraid of anyone, you are not afraid
of any one of them.

00:27:53.100 --> 00:28:00.550
Now about these people who have been troubling
you as fake gurus, I told about them in 1970.

00:28:00.550 --> 00:28:07.320
I'm just a lady and single-handed I told them
who these people are, how they are going to

00:28:07.320 --> 00:28:13.180
loot you, and what they are going to do; but
in this country nobody can think of one genuine

00:28:13.180 --> 00:28:16.120
person who could be really genuine.

00:28:16.120 --> 00:28:24.000
It was the problem that time, but with this
awakening within you of the virtuous nature,

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:26.340
you just know what is virtue and what is not
virtue.

00:28:26.340 --> 00:28:30.880
I don't have to tell you; I don't say “don't
do this, don't do that.”

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:38.551
I never say that, it just happens, because
when the virtue starts developing, the vibrations

00:28:38.551 --> 00:28:42.270
improve and you feel extremely joyous.

00:28:42.270 --> 00:28:52.110
We have lost our virtues because there is
no joy out of it, no reward.

00:28:52.110 --> 00:28:56.790
If somebody is honest, he has to suffer; if
somebody's good, he has to suffer; is somebody's

00:28:56.790 --> 00:29:04.820
kind, he thinks he has to suffer; but after
getting Realization you are rewarded for your

00:29:04.820 --> 00:29:05.820
virtues.

00:29:05.820 --> 00:29:10.900
You are amazed how you are paid for it, it’s
so surprising, like once there was a lady

00:29:10.900 --> 00:29:16.020
who came to see Me, she was a refugee, and
I had a big house.

00:29:16.020 --> 00:29:18.420
So I said, “All right come and stay with
Me.”

00:29:18.420 --> 00:29:21.340
So My husband, My brother they came, they
said, “What's this?

00:29:21.340 --> 00:29:24.920
You don't know her, who she is, her husband,
whether he is her husband or not, just given

00:29:24.920 --> 00:29:25.920
her two rooms.

00:29:25.920 --> 00:29:26.920
It's not good!”

00:29:26.920 --> 00:29:28.270
I said, “Let it be, doesn’t matter.

00:29:28.270 --> 00:29:31.330
I know for nothing is going to happen, let
her be here.”

00:29:31.330 --> 00:29:32.580
So they wouldn't also go against Me.

00:29:32.580 --> 00:29:33.850
They said, “All right, if you say so.”

00:29:33.850 --> 00:29:37.410
This lady stayed for ten days and went away.

00:29:37.410 --> 00:29:42.480
Then she become a very well-known actress
in India, I didn't know she was the same lady,

00:29:42.480 --> 00:29:44.860
but somebody told Me that she is the same
lady.

00:29:44.860 --> 00:29:45.860
I said, “Maybe.”

00:29:45.860 --> 00:29:51.130
Then one day you see, they wanted to make
a film for our Sahaja Yoga, so they said,

00:29:51.130 --> 00:29:54.580
“We can ask this lady to act, because she
is a good actress.”

00:29:54.580 --> 00:29:58.910
I said, “All right, you can go ask but don't
tell her I am here, otherwise she will have

00:29:58.910 --> 00:29:59.910
no choice.

00:29:59.910 --> 00:30:01.150
I will not go and see her.

00:30:01.150 --> 00:30:02.150
You just ask her.”

00:30:02.150 --> 00:30:05.580
They went and ask her, they said, “Will
you be actress?” and all that.

00:30:05.580 --> 00:30:06.580
She said, “I'll try.”

00:30:06.580 --> 00:30:07.580
This, that she was saying.

00:30:07.580 --> 00:30:12.250
But on the day on when they were going to
open the film I went there, she saw Me, she

00:30:12.250 --> 00:30:17.090
was so amazed, she said, “Oh God, You are
the One, You are the One Who is sponsoring

00:30:17.090 --> 00:30:18.880
this, Oh, I’ll give my life for Her!”

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:23.210
She just came forward, she said, “Have anything
you like, I have nothing to say, I am so sorry

00:30:23.210 --> 00:30:26.720
that you never told me that She's there.”

00:30:26.720 --> 00:30:32.340
Thousand times more she rewarded a little
thing I did for her.

00:30:32.340 --> 00:30:38.620
No more cheating, no more troubling, you become
a wonderful person and so many people become

00:30:38.620 --> 00:30:40.270
your friends in this world.

00:30:40.270 --> 00:30:44.770
Your have to just tell you are coming, there
will hundred people at the airport to receive

00:30:44.770 --> 00:30:45.770
you.

00:30:45.770 --> 00:30:49.460
There will be so many friends all over the
world for you, you will be amazed.

00:30:49.460 --> 00:30:55.130
It's such a tremendous thing happens, because
now you all are awakened in that Primordial

00:30:55.130 --> 00:30:58.350
Being and you have become one with each other.

00:30:58.350 --> 00:31:03.590
You can feel it, that oneness, that unison
that we are all not only human beings but

00:31:03.590 --> 00:31:08.230
we are yogis, we are super human beings, and
we have to look after the whole world.

00:31:08.230 --> 00:31:15.971
That feeling of compassion is so overwhelming
that all little, little stupid things just

00:31:15.971 --> 00:31:19.780
fall off, there's no place for that.

00:31:19.780 --> 00:31:22.880
This actually happens and has happened with
many.

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:27.390
Dr. Warren, whom you have seen here, can tell
you as I have told you lots of stories, but

00:31:27.390 --> 00:31:33.190
there are many, some of them were so hot tempered,
some of them were so quarrelsome, some them

00:31:33.190 --> 00:31:37.230
used to fight so much in the beginning that
I thought, “How are they going to be all

00:31:37.230 --> 00:31:38.230
right?”

00:31:38.230 --> 00:31:41.430
But today I find them as great friends and
very great yogis.

00:31:41.430 --> 00:31:47.590
So this is the center where your religion
is awakened.

00:31:47.590 --> 00:31:48.590
And what is a religion?

00:31:48.590 --> 00:31:52.770
Word comes from “religo,” in Sanskrit
it means dharma, “Dhariyatisa Dharma,”

00:31:52.770 --> 00:31:57.450
the sustenance, your sustenance, your valances
is your religion.

00:31:57.450 --> 00:32:03.200
As every atom, carbon has four valances, and
in the same way you have ten valances, these

00:32:03.200 --> 00:32:11.250
are the ten commandments that were told to
you and you become that, you just become.

00:32:11.250 --> 00:32:16.810
I don't have to tell you as commandments but
they become your beautiful ornaments within

00:32:16.810 --> 00:32:18.200
yourself.

00:32:18.200 --> 00:32:23.020
This happens automatically, so spontaneously
you become that.

00:32:23.020 --> 00:32:28.090
A bishop came to see Me the other day, he
is a relation of Mine, My brother.

00:32:28.090 --> 00:32:34.070
He came to see Me, and he was rather adamant
and little angry when he came to see Me because

00:32:34.070 --> 00:32:37.080
