00:32:41.500 --> 00:32:46.840
lectures in the church for years together,
but I could not achieve anything.

00:32:46.840 --> 00:32:49.600
How have You transformed these people?

00:32:49.600 --> 00:32:55.310
The drug addicts have suddenly become such
good people that they have given up drugs,

00:32:55.310 --> 00:32:56.850
alcoholics have given up alcohol.

00:32:56.850 --> 00:32:59.340
How is it without telling them anything?”

00:32:59.340 --> 00:33:01.370
