00:33:05.450 --> 00:33:08.820
You know that this is on your way, this is
against your progress, this is anti-life,

00:33:08.820 --> 00:33:10.500
you just give up.

00:33:10.500 --> 00:33:13.570
Only thing you have to have the light within
you.”

00:33:13.570 --> 00:33:20.280
So he himself was surprised at this and then
he said, “Really, that should be done, is

00:33:20.280 --> 00:33:21.340
to transform them.”

00:33:21.340 --> 00:33:26.230
But I said, “You do not transform them by
giving them big sermons, you transform them

00:33:26.230 --> 00:33:30.940
by giving them the real second birth, real
baptism.”

00:33:30.940 --> 00:33:37.080
And I must say that Calvinist, of all the
persons, Calvinist in Geneva have accepted

00:33:37.080 --> 00:33:41.170
Me and they think that this is the only way
they can transform you.

00:33:41.170 --> 00:33:48.280
You will be amazed the Calvinist of all the
persons who are such I should say one-sided

00:33:48.280 --> 00:33:56.000
people, they have accepted to see the result
of everybody who is open-minded person, who

00:33:56.000 --> 00:34:00.680
